title: Clemson-Alabama Draft Breakdown with Ryan Wilson (Football 1/08)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by NFL Draft expert Ryan Wilson to take a look at the CFP championship from a draft perspective. First the guys take a look at Matt Lafleur being hired by the Packers, other NFL news around the league and then they break down all the prospects from Clemson's 44-16 beatdown of Alabama.
